							<h5 class=" title bold t3 i_b_t3 mt40">성장만회를 위한 영양요구량</h5>
								<div>
									<ul class="mt10 pl15">
										<li class="i_box_t1">열량(kcal/kg)<br/>
											<img src="/images/sub/kcal_kg.PNG" alt="열량 계산법" title="계산법설명">
										</li>
